snippet.textDisplay:
Might as well answer these myself. Using SA-A-sA-sD-D-SD.
1. I am famous - SD. I mean seriously, I'm a random person on the internet.
2. Facetuning photos is completely fine - D. I can't stop you, but would certainly prefer it if you don't.
3. I wish I had someone else's YT channel instead - D. While it would be cool, I have next to no experience with the things that go into running a channel successfully. On top of that, I like the channels I like because of the people that run them. Taking their channel is taking something from them, and in turn taking something from myself.
4. I could date a girl that's had a threesome with 2 guys - SD. I'm a reserved person. If one isn't enough for you, you're too much for me. I'd also put a limit on how many people you've dated previously. Don't need someone who throws themselves at whoever they see fit that day.
5. I'm worried about the size of my penis - D. Plenty there, not the thing I'm worried about.
6. I regret a lot of videos I have released - D. I'm not proud of them, but I don't really regret them either.
7. The man should pay for dinner on the first date - sA. Definitely agree that the person who asked, should expect to pay though, but an offer to help out is certainly welcome. It shows that you actually care. Even if they decline, they know you care.
8. Likes and follows are important to me - D. I'm not gonna say I couldn't care less. It's still interesting to see what people think of the things I do.
9. I like meeting fans - sD. Pretty much exactly what Harry said, but probably even more awkward.
10. If doing YT earned no money, I would still post - SA. I mean, I don't get anything anyway. It's just fun to put something out there once in a while.
11. I could date a pornstar, if I were single - SD. Yeah, agree with all the points made.
12. One of the Sidemen is punching with their girlfriend - sA. I don't know them that well, but let's be honest here: probably true for one of 'em.
13. I only promote products I believe in - A. Don't get paid for promoting, everything I call good is good (in my opinion).
14. I need to have sex at least once a week - SD. #VirginGang?
15. I could date a fan - sD/D. It's just knowing that they have an admiration for you that you don't have for them, I guess. Unless I'm also a fan of their stuff, then that is cancelled out. I'm still a really picky person though, so it'd have to be The One for me to say yes.
